## ததஅக

[ iṉamoḻi ]  
  
பெ. id. indirectanswer which is not a straight reply to thequestion asked  
but a statement of somethingthat may be related to the subject of the question  
as  
for example  
when questioned haveyou pulses to sell  
to answer we have diamonds; one of eight kinds of viṭai  
q.v.; எண்வகை விடைகளுள் ஒன்று. (நன். 386.)